      <link>https://buenhyden.github.io/posts/software-engineering/design-and-architecture/design-patterns/gof/creational/factory-method-pattern/</link>
      <pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 18:21:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://buenhyden.github.io/posts/software-engineering/design-and-architecture/design-patterns/gof/creational/factory-method-pattern/</guid>
      <description>객체 생성을 위한 인터페이스를 정의하지만, 실제 어떤 클래스의 인스턴스를 생성할지는 서브클래스가 결정하도록 하는 디자인 패턴</description>
    </item>
    <item>
